description:
On July 31, Elon Musk posted that he accepted Venezuelan politician Nicolas Maduro's challenge for a fight. You can see the post here: https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1818683475530334368

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Venezuelan politician Nicolas Maduro and Elon Musk both announce that they have scheduled a date for a fight by August 9, 2024, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

For the purposes of this market, an “announcement” will be defined as Nicolas Maduro Elon Musk and Elon Musk publicly confirming that a physical fight will take place. The fight itself does not need to take place prior to August 9 for this market to resolve to "Yes".

The primary resolution source for this market will be any statements issued directly by both Nicolas Maduro and Elon Musk which confirm that a fight will take place.
